org.jnosql.artemis.graph

Interface EdgeTraversal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EdgeConditionTraversal

    public interface EdgeTraversal
extends EdgeConditionTraversal
    The Graph Traversal that maps Edge. This Traversal is lazy, in other words, that just run after any finalizing method.
